        {
            "title": "國際｜霍爾木茲海峽封鎖後 南韓船舶首次經紅海成功運油",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"國際｜霍爾木茲海峽封鎖後 南韓船舶首次經紅海成功運油\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">國際｜<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"霍爾木茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:霍爾木茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/霍爾木茲海峽\">霍爾木茲海峽</a>封鎖後 南韓船舶首次經紅海成功運油</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">韓聯社》報道，自霍爾木茲海峽遭封鎖以來，首次有南韓船舶通過紅海航道安全駛離。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據報該艘韓籍船舶在沙地阿拉伯延布港裝載原油後安全駛離紅海。南韓海洋水產部表示，將在考慮南韓船舶和船員安全的前提下，繼續與相關部門和業界合作，全力保障南韓船舶自中東運送原油回國。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">南韓總統李在明發文證實消息，並對船員等有關人士表示感謝。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E9%9C%8D%E7%88%BE%E6%9C%A8%E8%8C%B2%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96%E5%BE%8C-%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93%E8%88%B9%E8%88%B6%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E7%B6%93%E7%B4%85%E6%B5%B7%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E9%81%8B%E6%B2%B9-080514910.html",
